  "original_title": "Union Bank wins Most Campaign Partnerships award from Daraz",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Union Bank wins Most Campaign Partnerships award from Daraz",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Union Bank team (from left): Manager Business Development and Marketing \u2013 Cards Winu de Silva, Chief Manager Retails Assets and Cards Chamara Gomis and Assistant Manager Business Development \u2013 Cards Manuri Rodrigo receiving the award from Daraz CEO/Managing Director Rakhil Fernando and Head of Payments and Partnerships Dulika Jayamanne",
        "Union Bank for the second consecutive year was recognised at the Daraz Payment Partner Performance Awards and received the \u2018Most Campaign Partnerships\u2019 award this year in an event held on 28 July at Uga Residencies, Colombo.",
        "This award once again reaffirms Union Bank\u2019s continuous efforts to enhance credit card usage on e-commerce platforms and its efforts in developing new campaigns which contributed to developing the most number of campaigns on the Daraz platform by a bank for the year 2021-2022.",
        "The Daraz Payment Partner Performance Awards is an annual event for payment partners and rewards and recognises the contribution of bank partners towards the success of the platform\u2019s business growth. Since the inception of its partnership with Daraz, the bank has continuously introduced innovative campaigns to enhance the online shopping experience.",
        "An array of offers have been launched along with Daraz including, weekly discounts, offers on utility payments and partnering for special campaigns and extended payment plans such as the 11.11, Black Friday, Avurudu and Christmas Sales, etc. to reward the bank\u2019s cardholder base with an exciting online shopping experience. Daraz is South Asia\u2019s premier online shopping marketplace, backed by the global ecommerce giant, Alibaba Group, and has successfully brought together consumers and sellers to create Sri Lanka\u2019s largest e-commerce venue over the years.",
        "Union Bank Credit Cards are available in Gold, Platinum and Signature variants based on pre-set eligibility criteria."
      ],
